ReactJS Developer

HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, React, JavaScript, Git, SQL, Database

  • Visual Studio Code
  • Oracle
  • Firebase
  • MongoDB
  • Notepad++
  • Android Studio

Website Design

Things I enjoy designing:

UX, UI, Web, Apps

Design Tools:

  • Figma
  • Font Awesome
